item.description:
The Professionals of Color Business and Social Networking Meetup

January Meet-Up

This month we will be meeting socially to reintroduce ourselves to one another and meet new members.

I hope this will be an opportunity for the group to get to know one another and discuss plans for the new year.

I greatly appreciate your input. Please bring ideas for discussion topics, events and speakers and workshops.

Thank you all for your participation of the last year! I look forward to seeing you next week.

Qiana
